            "body" :"1 John is short enough to read in one sitting — about twenty minutes. The first chapter of this study includes the full text, and you are encouraged to read or listen to all five chapters before beginning. Seeing the whole letter at once makes each individual session significantly richer, and helps you see how John's recurring themes build and interweave."
